CHANGES
=======

1.3.9
-----

* Add mpls ip support on interface vlan

1.3.7
-----

* Add load-interval support on interface vlan

1.3.6
-----

* Add support for ip virtual-router addresses on arista

1.3.5
-----

* Add support for unknow interfaces in show interfaces
* Support the show interfaces switchport
* Show physical and vlan ports on show interfaces for Arista

1.3.4
-----

* Read multiple interfaces on show running-config interfaces
* Add switchport support with full error management
* Add ip helper-address support

1.3.3
-----

* Support for write memory

1.3.2
-----

* Support show interfaces
* Add the support for ip addresses (#140)
* Use a unique display object (#139)

1.3.1
-----

* Add default ports for transports services

1.3.0
-----

* Support empty reponses
* Add the support for errors in json format
* Add the support for the json version of show vlan
* Add a display driver mechanism
* Allow the show vlan command without being privileged
* Add the EAPI server layer for the arista switch
* Standardizing the transport instantiation
* Adding Arista driver for vlan management

1.2.5
